  "text": "Although in vitro and in vivo studies suggest that TiO 2 NPs cause various forms of pulmonary inflammation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , to our knowledge, relatively few studies have investigated the pulmonary effect in a rabbit model, and its pathogenic mechanism. The present study investigated the effect of TiO 2 NPs on rabbit lungs, evaluated by lung image analysis, bronchoalveolar lavage (BAL) fluids examination, and histopathologic analysis.",
